      • calculatePCTBehind

        public static double calculatePCTBehind​(double prevW,
                                        double currentW,
                                        double currentL,
                                        double prevL)
        Parameters:
        prevW - This is the number of wins of the top team already in the array
        currentW - The number of wins of the team that we want to compare to the top team to calculate PCT behind
        currentL - The number of wins of the team that we want to calculate their PCT behind
        prevL - The number of loses of the top team already in the array
        Returns:
        Returns the points behind the overall winning team for each of the other teams
